    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a family containing over 700 species in 11 genera of beetles that live in living vines and branches, dry wood, or under tree bark, some of which can damage or destroy structures or furnishings.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
